        "rent": 12530,
        "description": "Please note: This property can be booked with less bedrooms. Contact a Trip Designer for updated pricing.<br>Amilla Villa Estate is part of the UNESCO World Heritage Biosphere Reserve, in the Maldives’ Baa Atoll. This prestigious luxury rental has six beautiful bedrooms, an extremely generous amount of indoor and outdoor hosting spaces, a private beachfront, and an unparalleled view of the Indian Ocean.<br>This villa has everything you’ll need to feel at home while you’re on the island. The fully equipped kitchen with breakfast bar and formal dining for ten are perfect for hosting. The entertainment lounge is a great space to watch movies, play videogames, and challenge your friends to a table tennis match. Outside on the terrace you’ll find the swimming pool and hot tub. Lined with sun loungers, sun beds, and spacious outdoor living and dining areas, the terrace is the perfect place to relax in privacy or host an elegant island dinner party. The villa also includes breakfast, laundry service, housekeeping, and twenty-four hour security.<br>Amilla’s décor is simple and elegant. A bright and spacious atmosphere is created by predominantly using white. The vibrant blues, greens, and natural sunlight of the environment are the focal points. Cozy seating invites guests to relax in the tranquil indoor areas, while plenty of windows and openings let the ocean breeze flow freely throughout the interior. Several different balconies and outdoor living spaces make it easy to find a new spot to sit down with a glass of wine and enjoy the amazing ocean view.<br>All six of the bedrooms feature spectacular ocean views and their own ensuite bathrooms with stand-alone rain showers. Four of the bedrooms have king sized beds and private balconies, while the other two bedrooms are great for kids, one with a set of twins beds and the other with a single bed.<br>World class restaurants, shopping, and rejuvenating spas are just a short walk from the villa. If you’re feeling adventurous, there are plenty of excursions, water sports, and workshops to take part in at the estates beautiful facilities.<br>Copyright © Luxury Retreats. All rights reserved.<br><br><hr><br><b>BEDROOM & BATHROOM</b>        <ul style='list-style-type:disc'>                <li>Bedroom 1 - Master: King size bed, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower & bathtub, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Private balcony, Ocean view</li>        <li>Bedroom 2: King size bed, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Private balcony, Ocean view</li>        <li>Bedroom 3: King size bed, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Private balcony, Ocean view</li>        <li>Bedroom 4: King size bed, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Private balcony, Ocean view</li>        <li>Bedroom 5: 2 Twin size beds, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Private balcony, Ocean view</li>        <li>Bedroom 6: Single size bed, Ensuite bathroom with stand-alone rain shower, Lounge area, Television, DVD player, Ceiling fan, Direct access to terrace, Ocean view</li></ul><br><hr><br>        <b>FEATURES & AMENITIES</b><ul style='list-style-type:disc'>        <li>Fully equipped kitchen with breakfast bar<li>Formal dining area with seating for 10<li>Dishwasher<li>Wine fridge<li>Ice maker<li>Bar<li>Wi-Fi<li>Safes<li>Exercise area<li>Surround sound system<li>Entertainment/Lounge area<li>Television<li>DVD Player<li>DVD Library<li>Video games<li>Board games<li>PlayStation 4<li>Table Tennis<li>Ceiling fans<li>Washer & Dryer<li>Air conditioning<li>Security system</ul><br><hr><br>        <b>OUTDOOR FEATURES</b><ul style='list-style-type:disc'><li>Swimming pool & Hot tub</li><li>Sun loungers & sun beds</li><li>Outdoor dining area</li><li>Outdoor living area</li><li>Beachfront</li><li>Barbeque</li><li>Balcony</li><li>Terrace</li><li>Parking</li></ul><br><hr><br><b>STAFF & SERVICES</b><br>Included:<ul style='list-style-type:disc'><li>Airport transfer</li><li>Laundry service</li><li>Housekeeping service</li><li>24 hour Security Guard</li><li>Driving service (conditions may apply - please reference \"Need to Know\" section)</li><li>Breakfast</li><br>Extra cost (advance notice may be required):<br><ul style='list-style-type:disc'><li>Chef</li><li>Spa services</li><li>Villa pre-stocking</li><li>Babysitting Service</li><li>Activities & excursions</li><br><hr><br><b>LOCATION</b>        <br>        <b>Points of Interest</b><br>        Walking distance to Restaurants, shops & spas<br>        <b>Airport</b><br>        10 minute boat ride to Dharavandhoo Airport (DRV)<br>        90 km to Velana International Airport (MLE)        ",
